    "body": "When you use the test cert in grpc, you will need something like (C++):\r\n```\r\nchannel_args.SetSslTargetNameOverride(\"foo.test.google.fr\");\r\nchannel  = CreateCustomChannel(target, creds, channel_args);\r\n```\r\nYou can find examples in create_test_channel.cc."
